name: Here and Now
description: roll_01_shot_17 A '36 Shots' release for the Hic's #henosy Birthday celebration! Recife, Brazil 2017 // Happy half-birthday Hic. Oftentimes it feels like you are still birthing. This is a special photograph I’ve put aside for a special occasion. Shot in Brazil, Recife. And this man reminded me of you. On his own, battling the adventurous waters. Happy Birthday Hic, never stop birthing.// Ilford single use black and white camera. Part of '36 shots', a series of photographs all shot on single-use cameras. twitter: @edgar_dop insta: @edgardubrovskiy
